description: I own a few flats around Prague but I've never cared about my neighbors until now. Today I realized it was a big mistake. Maybe I don't have to search the streets, maybe there are cute dudes living next door. I was on my way outside when I bumped into this guy. He was busy preparing his rusty bike for a ride but was willing to chat. This innocent looking guy immediately made me horny as hell. I didn't hesitate and made him an offer. He was poor and easy. He whipped his huge semi right in the hallway of my apartment building and it cost me only 2 000 Crowns. Too bad the place was busy; I couldn't fuck him on the stairs so I took him to my flat. His naked body was nicely lean and covered in tattoos. This dude looked like an innocent angel and a criminal at the same time. I couldn't wait to start.
title: Czech Hunter 532
